name: Honey BBQ Chicken Wings Recipe | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Honey BBQ Chicken Wings Recipe: Chicken wings with skin ½ kg Flour 1 cup Eggs 2 Oil for fry Salt 1 tsp Honey ½ cup Barbecue sauce ½ cup Sesame seeds (roasted) 2 tbsp Garlic powder 1 tsp
instructions: Chicken wings cut in two pieces then add salt and garlic powder mix . Now coat in eggs and flour and fry for 6 to 8 minutes and set aside . Then in pan roasted sesame, honey, garlic powder. Add barbecue sauce, and 1 cup of water and cook for 5 minutes . Now fold chicken wings and serve it.
